<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>KiteCalc — Privacy Policy</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --text: #1a1a1a;
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --link: #0077B6;
      --muted: #666;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      :root {
        --text: #e5e5e5;
        --bg: #1a1a1a;
        --link: #4db8e8;
        --muted: #999;
      }
    }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--bg);
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }
    article {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      margin-top: 1.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    a {
      color: var(--link);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .subtitle {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <article>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="subtitle"><strong>KiteCalc</strong> — Kiteboarding Gear Calculator<br/>
    Effective date: April 9, 2026</p>

    <h2>Summary</h2>
    <p>KiteCalc does not collect, store, or share any personal data. Your privacy is simple: we don't take anything.</p>

    <h2>What We Collect</h2>
    <p><strong>Nothing personally identifiable.</strong> KiteCalc has no accounts, no login, no location tracking, and no advertising.</p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>KiteCalc uses <a href="https://telemetrydeck.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TelemetryDeck</a> for anonymous, privacy-first usage analytics. TelemetryDeck does not collect personal data. All user identifiers are hashed on-device before transmission, making it impossible to identify individual users. No IP addresses are stored.</p>
    <p>We use these anonymous signals solely to understand which features are used and to improve the app.</p>

    <h2>Advertising &amp; Tracking</h2>
    <p>KiteCalc does not use the Advertising Identifier (IDFA), does not display ads, and does not participate in any ad network. No App Tracking Transparency prompt is required because there is nothing to track.</p>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>All calculations are performed locally on your device. No data is sent to any server beyond the anonymous analytics signals described above.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>KiteCalc does not integrate with any third-party advertising, tracking, or data collection services beyond TelemetryDeck as described above.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>KiteCalc does not knowingly collect any data from children under the age of 13.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>If this policy changes, we will update this page with the new effective date.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? Reach out at <a href="mailto:kitecalc-privacy@danielrodriguez.name">kitecalc-privacy@danielrodriguez.name</a>.</p>
  </article>
</body>
</html>
